\c 32
\s Mashoko aErihu
\p
\v 1 Zvino varume ava vatatu vakaguma kupindura Jobho, nokuti waiva akarurama pameso pake\x + 31.6. 33.9.\x*.
\v 2 Zvino dzakapfuta hasha dzaErihu mwanakomana waBharakeri muBhuzi\x + Gen.. 22.21. Jer. 25.23.\x*, wedzinza raRami\x + Gen.. 22.21. Jer. 25.23.\x*; hasha dzake ndokupfutira Jobho nokuti waizviti iye wakarurama kupfuura Mwari\x + 4.17. 34.5. 35.2. 40.8.\x*.
\v 3 Uye hasha dzake dzakapfutira shamwari dzake nhatu, nokuti vaiva vashaiwa mhinduro, zvakadaro vakapa Jobho mhosva\x + 8.6. 15.20-35. 22.5.\x*.
\v 4 Zvino Erihu waiva akamirira Jobho pamashoko, nokuti vaiva vakuru kwaari pamazuva.
\v 5 Erihu paakaona kuti hapana mhinduro pamuromo wevarume ava vatatu, hasha dzake ndokupfuta.
\p
\v 6 Zvino Erihu mwanakomana waBharakeri muBhuzi wakapindura ndokuti: Ndiri mudiki pamazuva asi imwi muri vakuru\x + 15.10. 2 Makor. 36.17.\x*; saka ndakazvidzora ndikatya kukuzivisai\x + Map. 19.2.\x* pfungwa yangu\x + 32.10,17. 36.3. 37.16.\x*.
\v 7 Ndakati: Mazuva ngaataure, neuwandu hwemakore hudzidzise uchenjeri.
\v 8 Zvirokwazvo mweya urimo mumunhu\x + 33.4. 34.14.\x*, nekufema kweWemasimbaose\x + 35.11. 38.36. 39.17. 1 Madz. 3.12. 4.29. Zvir. 2.6. Mup. 2.26. Dhan. 1.17. 2.21. Jak. 1.5.\x* kunovapa kunzwisisa\x + 33.4. 34.14.\x*.
\v 9 Havazi vakuru vakachenjera\x + 32.7. Gen.. 25.23.\x*, kana vatana vanonzwisisa mutongo\x + 12.20. Mat. 11.25.\x*.
\v 10 Naizvozvo ndakati: Teererai kwandiri; neniwo ndicharatidza pfungwa yangu\x + 32.10,17. 36.3. 37.16.\x*.
\v 11 Tarirai, ndakamirira mashoko enyu; ndakapa nzeve kukunzwisisa kwenyu, pamaitsvaka mashoko.
\v 12 Zvirokwazvo ndakateerera kwamuri, zvino tarirai, hakuna pakati penyu wakapwisa Jobho, wakapindura mashoko ake\x + 38.18. 31.1.\x*.
\v 13 Zvimwe mungati: Tawana uchenjeri, ndiMwari achamudzinga, kwete munhu\x + 13.25.\x*.
\v 14 Asi haana kundirongedzera mashoko, uye nemashoko enyu handingamupinduri.
\v 15 Vakashamiswa, havachapinduri; vakabvisa manzwi kwavari.
\v 16 Zvino ndakamirira, asi havana kutaura, nokuti vakamira, havana kuzopindura.
\v 17 Neni ndichapindura chikamu changu\x + Eki. 18.4.\x*, neni ndicharatidza\x + 32.6.\x* pfungwa yangu\x + 32.10,17. 36.3. 37.16.\x*.
\v 18 Nokuti ndizere nemashoko; mweya wedumbu rangu unondishungurudza.
\v 19 Tarirai, dumbu rangu rakaita sewaini isina kuvhurwa, sehombodo itsva richaparuka\x + Mat. 9.17. Josh. 9.4.\x*.
\v 20 Ndichataura, kuti ndiremudzwe; ndichashamisa miromo yangu ndigopindura.
\v 21 Ndirege hangu kugamuchira chiso chemunhu\x + 42.8.\x*, uye handipi zita kumunhu\x + Isa. 44.5. 45.4.\x*.
\v 22 Nokuti handizivi kupa mazita; muiti wangu anondibvisa nekukurumidza\x + Isa. 44.5. 45.4.\x*.